---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Story | Sidharth Mohanty" description="The story behind the code">
  <section class="story-hero">
    <p class="hero-eyebrow">About Me</p>
    <h1 class="hero-title">
      The Story Behind
      <span class="title-accent">The Code</span>
    </h1>
    <!-- Wavy accent -->
    <svg class="wavy-accent" viewBox="0 0 120 12" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
      <path d="M2 6c4-4 8-4 12 0s8 4 12 0 8-4 12 0 8 4 12 0 8-4 12 0 8 4 12 0 8-4 12 0 8 4 12 0 8-4 12 0 8 4 12 0" stroke="url(#wavyGradStory)" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
      <defs>
        <linearGradient id="wavyGradStory" x1="0" y1="6" x2="120" y2="6">
          <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#6366f1"/>
          <stop offset="50%" stop-color="#a78bfa"/>
          <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#818cf8"/>
        </linearGradient>
      </defs>
    </svg>
    <p class="hero-tagline">Code. Build. Learn. Repeat.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="story-body">
    <div class="story-grid">
      <div class="intro-col">
        <h2 class="col-heading">About Sidharth</h2>

        <p class="body-text greeting">Hi there, I'm Sidharth</p>

        <p class="body-text">
          I'm a Software Engineer II at Builder.io, where I'm currently
          working on world-class software that empowers developers globally.
          I'm a fullstack developer with over 3 years of experience crafting
          applications that solve real problems.
        </p>

        <p class="body-text emphasis">
          Web apps, mobile apps, chrome extensions, APIs - I've explored them
          all. But here's the thing:
          <strong>I'm still learning every single day.</strong>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="details-col">
        <div class="detail-block">
          <h3 class="detail-heading">Technical Journey</h3>
          <p class="body-text">
            I've been a JavaScript enthusiast since day one. React, Vue,
            Angular, Node, Express, Nest, Next, Nuxt - I've danced with them
            all. I've also ventured into Golang and Python, creating APIs and
            CLI tools that bridge complex problems and elegant solutions.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="detail-block">
          <h3 class="detail-heading">Always Exploring</h3>
          <p class="body-text">
            Backend architecture, DevOps practices, database optimization,
            system design, CI/CD pipelines - curiosity drives my exploration.
            The tech landscape is vast, and I embrace that complexity with
            enthusiasm and systematic learning.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="detail-block">
          <h3 class="detail-heading">Beyond the Screen</h3>
          <p class="body-text">
            I'm a fitness enthusiast who believes in strengthening both mind
            and body. The gym is where I find balance. And coffee? It's the
            fuel that powers late-night coding sessions and early morning
            problem-solving marathons.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="milestones">
      <h2 class="milestones-heading">The Journey So Far</h2>
      <div class="milestones-grid">
        <div class="milestone-card">
          <span class="milestone-num">01</span>
          <h3 class="milestone-title">Student & Explorer</h3>
          <p class="milestone-desc">Computer Science at OUTR, Bhubaneswar</p>
        </div>
        <div class="milestone-card">
          <span class="milestone-num">02</span>
          <h3 class="milestone-title">Developer & Builder</h3>
          <p class="milestone-desc">3+ years crafting fullstack applications</p>
        </div>
        <div class="milestone-card">
          <span class="milestone-num">03</span>
          <h3 class="milestone-title">Open Source Contributor</h3>
          <p class="milestone-desc">Contributing to meaningful projects worldwide</p>
        </div>
        <div class="milestone-card">
          <span class="milestone-num">04</span>
          <h3 class="milestone-title">Continuous Learner</h3>
          <p class="milestone-desc">Always exploring new technologies and methodologies</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .story-hero {
    padding: 6rem 0 4rem;
    text-align: center;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease both;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .story-hero {
      padding: 8rem 0 5rem;
    }
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: #6366f1;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: 2.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .hero-title {
      font-size: 4rem;
    }
  }

  .title-accent {
    display: block;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #818cf8, #6366f1, #a78bfa);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .wavy-accent {
    width: 120px;
    height: 12px;
    display: block;
    margin: 0 auto 1.25rem;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .hero-tagline {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #71717a;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .story-body {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .story-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .story-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
      gap: 5rem;
    }
  }

  .col-heading {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: #71717a;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
  }

  .body-text {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: #a1a1aa;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .greeting {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #e4e4e7;
  }

  .body-text.emphasis {
    border-left: 2px solid #6366f1;
    padding-left: 1rem;
    color: #d4d4d8;
  }

  .body-text strong {
    color: #fafafa;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .detail-block {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .detail-heading {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #e4e4e7;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .milestones {
    padding-top: 3rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
  }

  .milestones-heading {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: #71717a;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .milestones-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .milestones-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .milestones-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .milestone-card {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
    transition: all 0.25s ease;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .milestone-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.25);
    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.04);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .milestone-num {
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #6366f1;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .milestone-title {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #e4e4e7;
    margin-bottom: 0.375rem;
  }

  .milestone-desc {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #71717a;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
